name: Nature's Call
desc: Converts an area of trees into Treants. Treants have 550 health and deal 30-34 damage.

name: Maledict
desc: Curses all enemy Heroes in a small area, causing them to take a set amount of damage each second, as well as bursts of damage every 4 seconds based on how much health they have lost since the curse began.

name: Reaper's Scythe
desc: Stuns the target enemy hero, then deals damage based on how much life it is missing. Heroes killed by Reaper's Scythe will have 15/30/45 seconds added to their respawn timer. Any kill under this effect is credited to Necrophos.\n\nUpgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

name: Rupture
desc: Causes an enemy unit's skin to rupture. If the unit moves, it takes a percentage of the distance traveled as damage.  The damage is dealt through spell immunity.\n\nUpgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

name: Skeleton Walk
desc: Clinkz moves invisibly through units until the moment he attacks or uses an ability.

name: Magic Missile
desc: Fires a magic missile at an enemy unit, stunning and dealing damage.

name: Chaotic Offering
desc: Summons a Golem from the depths, stunning enemies for one second. The Golem lives 60 seconds, takes reduced damage from spells, has Permanent Immolation and Flaming Fists on attack.\n\nUpgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

name: Geminate Attack
desc: Allows Weaver to dispatch two attacks at once.

name: Unstable Current
desc: Razor moves with increased speed, and hits a random nearby unit with a jolt of electricity every 5 seconds. The jolt deals damages, slows, and purges buffs from enemies.\n\nDISPEL TYPE: Basic Dispel

name: Eye of the Storm
desc: A powerful lightning storm strikes out at enemy units with the lowest health, dealing damage and reducing their armor.\n\nUpgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.
